data.name: label2.Text
data.value: Move into the pushup position on the floor. Keep your arms straight with your hand's shoulder width apart. Keep you head between your arms at all times.Lift your hips and move your legs closer, so your body perform the shape of an upside down V. Your legs and arms are to be as straight as possible. Inhale, as you bend at the elbows lowering your body until the top of the head, is nearly touching the floor and pause.Exhale and use your arms push your body back up until your a rms are straight again.
